>> source: Magnolia
>> serves: 1.5 cups

Combine 2 cups packed fresh @arugula{2%cups}; 3/4 cup shredded @Parmesan{3/4%cup} cheese; 2/3 cup @hopped toasted walnuts{2/3%cup}; 1/2 cup packed fresh @basil{1/2%cup}; 1/2 cup extra virgin @olive oil{1/2%cup}; 3 cloves @garlic{3%cloves}, halved; 1 tsp @lemon zest{1%tsp}; 2 Tbsp @lemon juice{2%Tbsp}; and 1/4 tsp kosher @salt{1/4%tsp} in a #food processor{}.

Process until nearly smooth. Add up to 2 Tbsp additional olive oil to reach desired consistency.
